<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>UEL(Thailand) Co., Ltd. cooperated with the Thai-Nichi Institute of Technology in the event "TNI Job Fair 2020" for introducing about CADmeister’s user companies in Thailand. There are various UEL (Thailand) ’s company partners who came to present their companies and available job positions, it was a great opportunity for the TNI newly graduated students who are looking for a suitable career. </p><p><br></p><p>The companies that collaborated with us </p><p><strong>1. <u>AWS Machinary& Santech Asia</u></strong></p><p><strong>2. <u>TamatsuuraPattern (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>3. <u>Horiuchi Technology(Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>4. <u>Toyoda Seiko (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><strong>5. <u>Nagano Precision (Thailand)</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Thank all of our partners and the Thai-Nichi Institute of Technology students that were interested in joining our event this time.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div>